div2.entryFree:

      قَرِيصٌ A kind of condiment, or seasoning;
(Lth, M, K;) called in the dial. of Keys قَرِيسٌ,
q. v. (TA.)


      قَشَّاطٌ A great spoiler, despoiler, or plunderer;
one who spoils, despoils, or plunders, much, or
frequently; syn. سَلَّابٌ. (TA.)


      قَوَدٌ ― 
       -b2-  قَتَلَهُ بِهِ قَوَدًا He slew him for him (i. e.
for the slain) in retaliation. (Msb.)
